            <!--SDSS-->
            <div class="card index-card outer" id="sdss">
                <div class="card-header collapsed card-sdss-purple" data-toggle="collapse" href="#sdssAccordion"
                     aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="sdssAccordion">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col">About the Sloan Digital Sky Survey</div>
                        <div class="col-auto plus-minus"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body bg-gray collapse" id="sdssAccordion" data-parent="#sdss">
                    <!--About SDSS content-->
                    <div>
                        <a href="https://www.sdss.org" target="_blank"><img src="/dr18/images/sdssIVlogo.png" class="sdss-thumbnail d-block mx-auto mb-2" alt="SDSS IV logo" /></a>
                    </div>
                    <p>
                        The <a href="https://www.sdss.org" target="_blank">Sloan Digital Sky Survey</a>, or
                        <a href="https://www.sdss.org" target="_blank">SDSS</a>,
                        is an international collaboration of scientists gathering data
                        from two telescopes in North and South America to build the most detailed
                        <a href="https://www.sdss.org/science/" target="_blank">Three-Dimensional Imagery</a> of the Universe ever made.
                        The SDSS has produced deep multi-color images of one third of the sky, and created spectra of more than three million
                        astronomical objects.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!--SciServer Card-->
            <div class="card index-card outer" id="sciserver">
                <div class="card-header collapsed card-blue" data-toggle="collapse" href="#sciserverList" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="sciserverList">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col">About SciServer</div>
                        <div class="col-auto plus-minus"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body collapse bg-gray" id="sciserverList" data-parent="#sciserver">
                    <div>
                        <a href="https://www.sciserver.org" target="_blank">
                            <img src="/dr18/images/sciserverlogo.png" class="sciserverlogo-thumbnail d-block mx-auto mb-2" alt="SDSS IV logo" />
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <p>
                        <a href="https://www.sciserver.org" target="_blank">SciServer</a>
                        is an NSF-supported project to build a big data platform that brings the computing to the data for
                        extremely large datasets. Using SkyServer with your free SciServer account unlocks additional features.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        SciServer hosts the following web-based apps that allow you to query and analyze your data in the cloud.
                    </p>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col text-center">
                            <a href="http://skyserver.sdss.org/CasJobs/" target="_blank">
