                    <img src="/dr18/images/sdssvoyages-icon.png" class="sdss-thumbnail d-block mx-auto mb-2" alt="Voyages Icon" />
                    <p>
                        <a href="http://voyages.sdss.org/" target="_blank">Voyages</a> is the educational website for the SDSS.
                        Voyages serves up projects, activities, resources, and research experiences for students of all ages
                        that build on data from the Sloan Digital Sky Survey.
                    </p>
                </div>
